{"tid":2270814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國以外交級別回應螞蟻事件 稱此等做法是為穩定資本市場","createTime":"2020-11-04T08:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T08:33:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04c0fa15330a18e680a88d94b21fef25edbf1c68","tid":2270814,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"外交部：暫緩螞蟻集團上市是為更好維護資本市場穩定<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌回應螞蟻集團暫緩上市時表示，暫緩決定是有關證券交易部門，履行自律監管責任的體現，暫緩上市則是有關交易機構根據有關法律法規，為了更好維護資本市場穩定和保護投資者權益而作出的決定。<br />\n<br />\n上海證券交易所昨晚暫緩螞蟻集團A股在上海科創板上市，螞蟻隨後亦暫緩本港H股上市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558328-20201104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558328-20201104.htm&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcyjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=76d2df18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558328-20201104.htm&h=e6a1ef96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558328-20201104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f1168b245721dcf4ceba3639ded855582d6cfdc4","tid":2270814,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:28:27.000Z","msg":"完全相反嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6837bf08127f1a39226500b786d3e8eafec2d234","tid":2270814,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"點解用外交部講？金融呢啲事"},{"pid":"9260fcbe92b41d0827feb794ededdd62a2ac43fd","tid":2270814,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:30:21.000Z","msg":"支那有資本市場既咩"},{"pid":"fc446438e095fc57068ef9cfbdbd7b688318dd91","tid":2270814,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6837bf08127f1a39226500b786d3e8eafec2d234","tid":2270814,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"點解用外交部講？金融呢啲事"},"citedBy":0,"replyT